Author: 54y95s785
Text: It took me a long time to figure out that when normal people say "I barely ate today!" "omg I haven't eaten all day" "this is my first meal lol," which we know that a lot of people do, they don't mean it the same way we do. I spent so long feeling jealous and shitty and competitive when people did this sort of thing, only to find out that their idea of not eating all day was basically the sort of thing your brother described. life is mad, huh
